						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up near the well called Kallappana-bhāvi at the old ruined village.</p>						

						<p>1160 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Pramādi, Māgha ba. 6, Sitavāra. The record may be assigned to the 12th century when the details correspond to 1160 A.D., January 29, Friday f.d.t. °68.</p>						

						<p>It records the death of Śānti-paṇḍita who had built the shrine of Mallinātha at Iṅgaḷēśvara.</p>						

						</summary>
